author: Atomic Shrimp
description:
This is a walk in the hills and by the water around the town of Bala on the edge of Eryri National Park (Snowdonia).
This is one of a series of videos recorded during our week-long stay in early September at Llangollen in the Dee Valley in Wales.

I said I would link to a bilberry video, so here's one of those: https://youtu.be/-ukT4DzjjB0

Join the Atomic Shrimp official Discord server for FREE early access to videos! - https://discord.gg/atomicshrimp

title: A Hillside Walk Around Bala and Llyn Tegid (and a Simple, Hearty Lamb Stew to Follow)
